name: Sara Demarans
description: I’m Sara by name and i’m a sensitive, curious and open minded person, who likes to meet new people and make friends from all around the world. I really want to try be in a relationship, I believe in the importance of honesty, love, friendship and truth. Therefore I would like to meet people who are thinking the same way. To have good friends and a family who loves you, gives you the foundation to live a positive life and be strong during hard times.
